videos.headline: Taylor rumbles in for Badgers' TD
videos.description: Jonathan Taylor finds a hole and scores the touchdown from 13-yards out.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Taylor rumbles in for Badgers’ TD) 2019/09/28

videos.headline: Northwestern's Pace picks off Coan
videos.description: Wisconsin's Jack Coan tries to go deep but he is intercepted by Northwestern's JR Pace.

videos.headline: Badgers get defensive TD off fumble recovery
videos.description: Wisconsin's Eric Burrell knocks the ball loose from the Northwestern QB and it is recovered by Matt Henningsen for the touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Badgers get defensive TD off fumble recovery) 2019/09/28

videos.headline: Wisconsin's Burks grabs tipped ball for 68-yard pick-6
videos.description: Wisconsin's Noah Burks picks off the pass and then tight ropes the sideline for the 68-yard pick-6.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Wisconsin's Burks grabs tipped ball for 68-yard pick-6) 2019/09/28

videos.headline: Wisconsin forces 3rd turnover of the day
videos.description: Wisconsin linebacker Chris Orr crushes the Northwestern QB causing a fumble which is recovered by the Badgers.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Wisconsin forces 3rd turnover of the day) 2019/09/28

videos.headline: Northwestern cuts into Badgers' lead with a TD
videos.description: Northwestern's backup QB Aidan Smith rolls right and finds JJ Jefferson in the end zone for the touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Northwestern cuts into Badgers' lead with a TD) 2019/09/28

videos.headline: Badgers' defense dominates in win over Northwestern
videos.description: Wisconsin's defense scores two touchdowns and forces three turnovers to lead the Badgers to a 24-15 win over Northwestern.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Badgers’ defense dominates in win over Northwestern) 2019/09/28 SOTFULL
